Objective: Replace the page that will not be used for the longest time in the future.

Algorithm:

Initialize frame[] with -1.
For each page ref[i]:
Check if ref[i] is in frame[].
If yes → no page fault.
If no → page fault occurs:
For each frame, look ahead in ref[i+1] ... ref[n-1]:
Find the frame whose page appears farthest in the future or does not appear at all.
Replace that frame with ref[i].
